            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Berta"/>Berta</persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Morentianus">Morentano</name></persName>, con il consenso dei
                        suoi mundualdi <persName><name ref="Walfredus">Walfridi</name></persName> e
                                <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName>, vende a
                            <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Leo">Leone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abate</rs> del <rs key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/71"
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Monasteries">San Ponziano</orgName>
                        di <placeName ref="#places/4">Lucca</placeName>, ad parte della <rs
                            key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3111"
                            key="#Churches">San Salvatore</orgName> de loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/180">Vaccule</placeName> que est im potestate et
                        proprietate del suddetto monastero, quartam portionem de medietatem di un
                        appezzamento di terra, quod est casalino et orto atque vinea, posto nello
                        stesso luogo prope la suddetta chiesa, <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> unum caput in via
                        publica, aliud caput con terra del <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">fu Sona(...)</persName> latus (...)
                        con tutte le sue dipendenze, ricevendo <rs key="#Meritum/launechild"
                            >meritum</rs> pro 10 soldi da <persName><name ref="Rusticus"
                                >Rustico</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martino</name></persName>. Chiede al <rs key="#Notary #Writer"
                            >notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Cuneradus"
                            >Corrado</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum Luca. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: g. <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudatus">Teudato</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Morentianus">Morentano</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Signorectus"
                            >Signoretto</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Werro"
                                >Guerro</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rusticus">Rustico</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
